getEdgeComparator

public static java.util.Comparator<Edge> getEdgeComparator(java.util.Comparator<Node> cmp)
Produce an edge comparator from a node comparator.

Produce an edge comparator that is based on the lexicographic order of the pair of nodes associated with an edge.

Note that this can create a comparator that is not consistent with equals in the case of undirected edges.

Returns:
an edge comparator.
